Leetcode problem- https://leetcode.com/problems/largest-perimeter-triangle/

Q.) Given an integer array nums, return the largest perimeter of a triangle with a non-zero area, formed from three of these lengths. 
    If it is impossible to form any triangle of a non-zero area, return 0.
    
Solution- 

    public int largestPerimeter(int[] nums) {
        Arrays.sort(nums);
        for(int i=nums.length-1; i>1; i--){
            if(nums[i]<(nums[i-1]+nums[i-2])){
             return nums[i]+nums[i-1]+nums[i-2];
            }
        }
        return 0; 
    }
